  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    gobblin.source.Source<org.apache.avro.Schema,org.apache.avro.generic.GenericRecord>

    public class DatePartitionedDailyAvroSource
extends FileBasedSource<org.apache.avro.Schema,org.apache.avro.generic.GenericRecord>
    Implementation of Source that reads over date-partitioned Avro data.

    For example, if ConfigurationKeys.SOURCE_FILEBASED_DATA_DIRECTORY is set to /my/data/, then the class assumes folders following the pattern /my/data/daily/[year]/[month]/[day] are present. It will iterate through all the data under these folders starting from the date specified by DATE_PARTITIONED_SOURCE_MIN_WATERMARK_VALUE until either DATE_PARTITIONED_SOURCE_MAX_FILES_PER_JOB files have been processed, or until there is no more data to process. For example, if DATE_PARTITIONED_SOURCE_MIN_WATERMARK_VALUE is set to 2015/01/01, then the job will read from the folder /my/data/daily/2015/01/01/, /my/data/daily/2015/01/02/, /my/data/2015/01/03/ etc.

    The class will only process data in Avro format.
